text: dau che neah yeung ban banhchea tha chaur puok anak yk phnek namuoy nei meko nih veay towleu sakasap noh . dauchnih der a l laoh nung thveu aoy anak slab teangoasa rsa laengvinh( now thngai barlok) haey a l laoh bangheanh ph so d tang robsa trong dl puok anak daembi aoy puok anak cheh kitpichearna
